# nl-rag distilled facts — domain: fred-corey
# one declarative sentence per line; load with:  neuron --db app.db import pack.facts --scope knowledge
[src:fred-corey/1878-in-baseball] The following are the baseball events of the year 1878 throughout the world.
[src:fred-corey/1878-in-baseball] Inter-league playoff: Boston (NL) and Buffalo (IA) each won 1 game in 2-game series.
[src:fred-corey/1880-in-baseball] The following are the baseball events of the year 1880 throughout the world.
[src:fred-corey/1882-in-baseball] The following are the baseball events of the year 1882 throughout the world.
